with someone, there always gonna be differences

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:13.170
between one person and anotha. And even if
it’s a fat-ass social gap like da one between

00:05:13.170 --> 00:05:17.440
da Greasers and da Socs, there’s always
a chance to build a bridge and pave it with

00:05:17.440 --> 00:05:18.600
gold, playa.

00:05:18.600 --> 00:05:23.270
In fact, da poem “Nothing Gold can Stay”
by Robert Frost gets a shoutout in da book

00:05:23.270 --> 00:05:25.280
dat schools Pony boy real good.

00:05:25.280 --> 00:05:28.530
“I’ve been thinking
about it, and that poem, that guy that wrote

00:05:28.530 --> 00:05:32.200
